title: Goodbye... Fancypants! Timing malfunction.
description: The Master! He's out there. I've got to stop... him... Bow ties are cool. The thing is, Adam, time travel is like visiting Paris. You can't just read the guidebook, you've got to throw yourself in! Eat the food, use the wrong verbs, get charged double and end up kissing complete strangers! Or is that just me? Well Kangs, I must say, there's no place like home... and this is no place like home. This stuff, or whoever sent it, is cleverer than we are. Unfortunate, isn't it?
